Hi guys, today we are unboxing this new battery powered Kid Trax 12-Volt Captain America Motorcycle Ride-On.
Join the Avengers for hours of driveway fun on the 12-Volt Marvel Captain America Motorcycle Ride-On from Kid Trax! This tough toy motorcycle will be a hit for any Avengers fans out there. Just like Captain America and Bucky ride, this motorcycle is perfect for your little hero and their trusty sidekick. The sidecar is removable and easy to attach again when it's playdate time. Hydra doesn't stand a change against the dart launcher and included soft rubber-tipped darts. We had so much fun in this cool ride on especially driving my little brother around.
